moduleMetadataJson.name: SIP Deregister Extension
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module will attempt to deregister a SIP user from the provider. It
        has been tested successfully when the sip provider/server doesn't use REGISTER
        authentication.
author: ChrisJohnRiley

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: THREADS
options.description: The number of concurrent threads (max one per host)

options.name: ShowProgress
options.description: Display progress messages during a scan

options.name: ShowProgressPercent
options.description: The interval in percent that progress should be shown

options.name: SRCADDR
options.description: The sip address the spoofed deregister request is coming from

options.name: EXTENSION
options.description: The specific extension or name to target
